(2682, 1, '2018-03-10 10:51:46', '2018-03-10 10:51:46', '<p>Welcome to J\'s Big Gym.</p><p>J\'s Big Gym is proud to be the FIRST in Home Mobile Personal Training and Fitness Franchise Company. As #1 in Home Personal Training, we offer individualized one-on-one workouts, group instruction and corporate fitness. J\'s Big Gym has an amazing team of certified coaches that incorporate the J\'s Big Gym philosophy of the 3 Cs during each workout.&nbsp;</p><p>Our workouts are Convenient, Customized &amp; Creative. For your convenience, we travel to you in our J\'s Big Gym van to your home, office, park or setting of your choice, at a time that works best for you. Each van is stocked with state of the art fitness equipment enabling the J\'s Big Gym coach to provide you with your customized workout. Our certified coaches are trained using the J\'s Big Gym methodologies.&nbsp;</p><p>We utilize the tools and techniques required for a creative exercise program with high quality service. No two workouts are ever the same! J\'s Big Gym is not like any other gym or fitness program. We have no membership fees, the first visit is always free and the initial assessment includes a body assessment, fitness assessment and a nutrition assessment.</p><p>We welcome all individuals of all levels regardless of experience, age or ability. Each client is reassessed every 15 weeks to ensure that you are exceeding your goals. J\'s Big Gym teaches lifelong habits that will keep you looking and feeling your best.</p><p><b>Our Mission:</b> Improve the health and quality of life for people through personalized, accessible wellness programs<br></p>', 'J\'s Big Gym', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'js-big-gym', '', '', '2020-07-16 08:05:04', '2020-07-16 08:05:04', '', 0, 'https://listing.downtown-directory.com/backup/?post_type=listing&#038;p=2682', 0, 'listing', '', 2),
(2710, 1, '2018-03-12 07:38:39', '2018-03-12 07:38:39', 'Kastel Bar &amp; Restaurant, Bar, Lounge, located in the heart of Nyack, NY, serves fine Italian cuisine. With over 25 years of experience in Bergen and Rockland County, we found a way to combine superior service with the utmost quality. Every item on the menu is made to order, using only the freshest ingredients. Our kitchen is open from 10 AM to 1 AM.&nbsp;<p>Come for dinner, stay for drinks! Kastel Bar &amp; Restaurant is the perfect spot for a family dinner, date night, or ladies/guys night out. Indulge in one of our signature cocktails, check out our extensive beer selection, and be sure to catch our 2 for 1 happy hour from 3 PM to 6 PM. Never miss a game again! With our 20 plasma televisions, we feature all of the sports packages. Live music and DJs throughout the week. Ask us about our upstairs VIP lounge. Perfect for all special occasions.</p><p>We are the leader in the Southern Tier for Banquets, Weddings and Special Events. We can accomadate for over 450 people including a 30 seat bar with a private dance floor. Our chef, Joe Spaziani, graduated in 1979 from the world famous Culinary Institute of America in Hyde Park, New York. Superb recipes encounterd around the world have been adopted and in some cases improved upon here at Kastel Bar &amp; Restaurant. Some dishes are purely original creations, having been created in our kitchen.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p>', 'Kastel Bar & Restaurant', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'kastel-bar-restaurant', '', '', '2020-07-16 08:05:17', '2020-07-16 08:05:17', '', 0, 'https://listing.downtown-directory.com/backup/?post_type=listing&#038;p=2710', 0, 'listing', '', 2),
